{
  "stem": "214.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and why is it-- you know, we-- really, when I think of it now that we had-- we talked all night long.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were just sitting there and talking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, now you know, our hearts are probably going like sitting about-- about maybe.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "About 3 o'clock in the morning, maybe, we heard-- you know, they started shooting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then this-- some man that-- I think he was a Pole-- came in and brought this suitcase, and left, and told us, in 10 minutes or in 15 minutes we would walk out-- I mean, not together, of course-- and go to the railway station and-- and come to-- if all goes well, pick up.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then I found out-- and, you know, and that was bad-- that I was-- we were talking, and talking, and talking.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then when we came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We took the train and everything and went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there I found out that this suitcase was full of money-- I don't know, maybe dollars.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, dollars was a commodity, which was-- and, you know, and this fellow, he was so happy that everything went pass.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we arrived, it was early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he insisted that he wants to treat me to breakfast.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And before I even-- this, I remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I felt so badly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Before I even went home to the-- but I'm-- you know, later on when I was considering, and now when I think of it, too-- though, for my-- for my mother-- my father was not alive anymore.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For-- no, he was still alive that time until the 24th of August.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But for my parents, you know, this waiting was much more.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I was in the situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
